{"word":"ἐξέλκω","slug":"ἐξέλκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξέλκω</b></el> <el>(aor1 <el>-είλκῠσα</el>) (3rd sg. <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <a href='S:subjunctive mood'>subj.</a> <el>-ελκυσθῇ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to draw</i> or <i>drag out</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to drag out from</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to drag along</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}